public interface StructuredFlow
extends SingleSuccessorFlow, TaskFlow

A Flow which can contain other flows. This kind of flows have a single entry point (initialFlow) and a single exit point (finalFlow), and can contain one or several internal branches.

Author:
Yeray Callero
